Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you agree with, you join\Nwith. So the bystander who eggs people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,on thinks they're escap escaping the\Nkarmic consequences but they are not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And we see that because when they come\Nback you see whole ethnic groups wiped
