Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.79,0:21:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,what what's the difference? A a doctor\Ndoctor
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,um a doctor doctor calibrates probably\Nis practicing medicine at about 440
