Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,than that below it. So there's the\Nacademic medical practitioner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there is the healer\Nwho is usually holistic and willing to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything to help a patient. And I\Nremember having to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.64,0:22:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this patient sitting in front of\Nme in the office, desperately ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing everybody in the world and\Nhopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to make a decision then. Was I\Ngoing to stick to academic medicine and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,gain the approval of my colleagues or\Nwas I going to try non-traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,healing techniques and lose their\Napproval? And I thought on deathbed I
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.36,0:23:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,am answerable to God.\Nfor this patient. This soul lord
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,he's given to me to heal. So\NI made that decision.
