Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.08,0:23:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everywhere. They'd fly him in from Paris\Nor whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uganda, God knows where. And uh as he's\Nsitting there talking to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in the back of my mind, he's hopeless\Nschizophrenic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.60,0:24:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All the anticychotics have been tried.\NAnd as he's talking, I'm thinking to
