Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.36,1:44:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,great. And if not in your pickup truck\Nwhere your shotgun goes,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.40,1:44:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you can hang it on that rack there.\NBut I did have a question for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.32,1:44:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uh relating to the course of miracles.\N>> When you took the course of miracles,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.63,1:44:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what was the biggest blockage that you\Nhad in absorbing the information at the
Dialogue: 0,1:44:55.36,1:44:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,time?\N>> I didn't have any. I was just uh
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.60,1:45:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,enthused about it.\NAnd um sometimes the phrasiology I would
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.40,1:45:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,have to think out the phrasiology\Nbut the basic concept was already
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.96,1:45:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential. You see\Nyou see you see things differently.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:23.36,1:45:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you see people as innocent, then you\Ndon't have to worry about hating them or
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.11,1:45:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,being angry or revenge because you see,\Nthey can't help being anything other
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.32,1:45:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,than what they are at this point in\Ntheir evolution. Huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.08,1:45:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any resistance to anything\Nin it.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.23,1:45:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Wanted to thank you for everything\Nyou've done for the last four years for
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.28,1:45:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,us. It's been wonderful.\N>> Thank you.
