Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.67,1:45:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.\N>> No, no, no, no. I shouldn't say that as
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.92,1:46:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,a joke.\NActually, it's five. Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.15,1:46:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,>> yeah.\N>> Thank you.
